{"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[103.72234,13.6351416]},"properties":{"addr:city":"Romiet, Nokor Pheas, Angkor Chum, Siem Reap","description":"According to satellite imagery, there appears to be a circular village, that are likely to be traces of an ancient settlement. To the northeast is a rectangular man-made reservoir that we have listed as C1701144, and 250m to the northwest is Prasat Chrani","name":"Phum Romiet   (Ancient Village)","name:km":"ភូមិរមៀត","note":"13.63536, 103.72248\nPart of\tPhum Romiet","place":"village"}}
